                            <comment id="13142692" author="hudson" created="Wed, 2 Nov 2011 23:43:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Thrift #314 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Thrift/314/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Thrift/314/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
